    </div>

    <div class='span4 clearfix'>
      <h2 class='center-header'>Resource Exchange <small>share files</small></h2>
      <p>Registered members can upload relevant resources to CPLAAC, which can then be shared amongst peers. You can also download the resources other members have shared.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='span4 clearfix'>
      <h2 class='center-header'>Directory <small>find LAC services</small></h2>
